name: First Congregational Church of Wakefield, NH
directions: Most likely, you'll be entering through the side door; if so, go through the door on the right and up the stairs one level. Go through the next door into the narthex (lobby of the sanctuary) and cross the narthex to find the bathroom door by the window, across from the coat rack.
comment:
Only available at certain times - generally, 9--2 on weekdays and 9-12 on Sundays. The bathroom door locks, there are blinds on the windows, there should be a horizontal metal bar to support you, and a changing table is present. Everything should be present, but in case some supplies are missing you can check the cabinet in the room, but please put things back as you found them. With Love,
Max
